715657f-b.title: Manhattan: 149th Street - Amsterdam Avenue
715657f-b.text:
(1)
149th Street, Eastward from near Amsterdam Avenue, showing
Church of the Crucifixion.
(2)
149th 5treet, Westward from St. Nicholas Avenue, showing
Hamilton Garage, Reformed Ghurch on corner of Convent Avenue.
P.L.Speer.
NO REPROLUCTION.  May 19, 1940.
